a sample rails app in front of the OCSinventory Database (http://www.ocsinventory-ng.org/)

This small application is just a concept and display informations 
of hosts register in ocs mysql database


# $ git clone http://github.com/pli01/ocsinventory-rails.git
# $ cd ocsinventory-rails
# Review config/database.yml and modify as needed
# $ rake db:migrate
# $ rake db:seed
# $ ruby script/server
# Point your browser to http://localhost:3000/dashboard

